  messages:
  - Welcome to your VR rooml Use the primary button or touch the joystick to toggle
    your rays. Aim at the Next button and pull the trigger to continue.
  - Press the secondary button on your controller at any time to reset the scene
    to its default state.
  - Aim your ray at rugs around the room and press the Grip button to teleport. Enjoy
    youriVR room!
